  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CompositeEntityI<T>
    A class containing basic methods for handling data of entities with two foreign keys.
    DaoI<T>
    The most basic methods for handling database data
    PlainEntityI<T>
    A class containing basic methods for handling data of entities with no more than one foreign key.
